subject: College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Kyle Singler had 19 points as No. 8 Duke opened its season with an 80-49 rout of Presbyterian in the first round of the 2K Sports Classic. Duke won its 60th straight nonconference game at Cameron Indoor Stadium. In the other game there, Georgia Southern beat Houston, 65-63, in the first regular-season game of the season.
